ADT API

API and SDK Documentation

Version: 1.0.0

Official & Core API for ADT [ADT](http://adtcore.io) Main API

Default

drugsDrugIdDelete

Deletes the drug specified by drugId


/drugs/{drugId}

Usage and SDK Samples

  • Curl
  • Java
  • Android
  • Obj-C
  • JavaScript
  • C#
  • PHP 

curl -X delete "https://virtserver.swaggerhub.com/BrianPhiri/ADT-CORE/1.0.0/drugs/{drugId}"




import io.swagger.client.*;
import io.swagger.client.auth.*;
import io.swagger.client.model.*;

import java.io.File;
import java.util.*;

public class DefaultApiExample {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        
        DefaultApi apiInstance = new DefaultApi();
        Long drugId = 789; // Long | Particular Service at facility specified by the ID
        String apiKey = apiKey_example; // String | 
        try {
            apiInstance.drugsDrugIdDelete(drugId, apiKey);
        } catch (ApiException e) {
            System.err.println("Exception when calling DefaultApi#drugsDrugIdDelete");
            e.printStackTrace();
        }
    }
}

drugsDrugIdDoseGet

Find drug dose for drugId

Returns the dose for the drug with the specified drugId


/drugs/{drugId}/dose

Usage and SDK Samples

  • Curl
  • Java
  • Android
  • Obj-C
  • JavaScript
  • C#
  • PHP 

curl -X get "https://virtserver.swaggerhub.com/BrianPhiri/ADT-CORE/1.0.0/drugs/{drugId}/dose"




import io.swagger.client.*;
import io.swagger.client.auth.*;
import io.swagger.client.model.*;
import .DefaultApi;

import java.io.File;
import java.util.*;

public class DefaultApiExample {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        
        DefaultApi apiInstance = new DefaultApi();
        Long drugId = 789; // Long | ID of service that needs to be fetched
        try {
            DrugDose result = apiInstance.drugsDrugIdDoseGet(drugId);
            System.out.println(result);
        } catch (ApiException e) {
            System.err.println("Exception when calling DefaultApi#drugsDrugIdDoseGet");
            e.printStackTrace();
        }
    }
}

import io.swagger.client.*;

import io.swagger.client.model.*;

import java.util.*;

public class DefaultApiExample {

        DefaultApi apiInstance = new DefaultApi();
        Long serviceId = 789; // Long | ID of service that needs to be fetched
        Long regimenId = 789; // Long | ID of service that needs to be fetched
        try {
            PatientRegimen result = apiInstance.servicesServiceIdRegimensRegimenIdGet(serviceId, regimenId);
            System.out.println(result);
        } catch (ApiException e) {
            System.err.println("Exception when calling DefaultApi#servicesServiceIdRegimensRegimenIdGet");
            e.printStackTrace();
        }
    }
}
